AboutMeParts.Second: I am 26 years old and live in Roskilde. I have a big interest for programming and technology. I am a previously trained EUX electrician, specializing in BMS (Building Management System)

MyGoals.Title: My goals
MyGoals.Goals: My goals are to expand my knowledge in programming and system development. As well as gaining experience in using what I have learned from my time on the Computer Science course at Zealand Roskilde

ChannelCrm.Text-1: During my internship as a computer scientist, I was an intern at ChannelCrm. ChannelCrm is a company located in KÃ¸ge and specializes in delivering CRM systems.
ChannelCrm.Text-2: During the stay, I helped renew the old system to a new .NET Blazor system. In addition to creating the frontend and backend in .NET Blazor, I have also worked on converting the old Microsoft Silverlight database to fit the new system's SQL Express database.
